name: Classic Wah
details:
Wah PedalThis wah has a sweet, musical, vintage tone and buyers are surprised at just how well this wah pedal delivers the goods. The Rocktron Classic Wah has a heavy duty, all metal chassis with tension adjustment for the pedal.
Power Supply - AC Adapter, Battery
Output - Impedance1 K ohms
Input - Impedance1 M ohms
Current Draw - 35 mA
Nominal Input - 10 dBu
